{
  "stem": "4963.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we were forewarned that the ghetto was going to be liquidated and that they were going to place all of us-- they were going to evacuate us all to Poland and Germany, to Stutthof, Dachau, you know, at the time we didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But eventually we knew it was to the camps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So panic, really, I remember people becoming very, very panicky and-- and starting to to think of what to do, where to go, to plan, you know, how to-- how to survive.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was your family in a panic?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did your--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, my family was very much in a panic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember we had the huddles-- the meetings that night and-- and starting to talk amongst, you know, everybody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the children were involved, too, as to what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- my [INAUDIBLE], my uncle took his son out, who as at the time I think like three-- to a-- to a-- well, he must have been four, four and a half-- to a Lithuanian family.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] go out in the workforce and hide-- you know, go-- take the child under a coat, under a jacket, or perhaps in a bag, you know, someplace that was-- that was hidden, and the workforce many times consisted of five, six people in a lineup.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so, again, by alerting the committee members, they would watch out that-- that they were in the middle and that--",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This happened 1943.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was-- I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When my-- when my little boy was taken out of the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I do remember that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
